column5: Been awhile since I purchased bait near quinte... Who sells dew worms out that way?
If your gonna be around Hay Bay I'm pretty sure Pickerel Park on the south shore sells bait Greg, but it's been a few years since I was there.
Pro Tackle has worms in Belleville.Take the 37 hwy exit  north for 1 mi. of the 401. He is on the right hand side.
Gagnon's in Oshawa sells worms if you are passing that way...
There will be tons on the lawn tonight after the rain
